Package: libudev++
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Description: udev++ – a Udev Library for C++
 The udev++ library is a lightweight C++ wrapper for libudev. It allows one to
 enumerate, monitor and introspect devices on the local system.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

