 libudev++ (= ${binary:Version}),
Description: libudev++ – an OSC Library for C++
 The udev++ library is a lightweight C++ wrapper for libudev. It allows one to
 enumerate, monitor and introspect devices on the local system.
 .
 This package contains development files.
